quote.summary: BBSB International Limited is a civil engineering contractor in Malaysia. It is focused on provision of construction services in Malaysia. It specializes in providing bridge engineering services as a subcontractor for large-scale transportation infrastructure engineering projects. Its bridge engineering services primarily involve the design and construction of the entire girder bridge or any one or more of its sections with various structural configurations and across roads and rivers, together with the construction of connecting highways, roads and ancillary facilities related to the bridge. Its services include bridge engineering works and flood mitigation works. It is focused on the design and construction of flood mitigation structural solutions to reduce flooding risks in urban and flood-prone areas. Its projects include Project JB27, Project JB28, Project JB29, and Project JB31. Project JB27 is a federal highway project spanning approximately 340KM across Peninsular Malaysia.
